flowchart TD
    A[Planner output: command batch] --> B[Queue ingestion]
    B --> C[Build queue items with task contract snapshot]

    C --> D{Mutability}
    D -->|readonly| R1[ready]
    D -->|mutating| P0[PreflightRequest]

    P0 --> L1[Layer 1: Contract and schema gate]
    L1 --> L1D{L1 decision}
    L1D -->|hard_block| F1[failed: contract or schema]
    L1D -->|pass| V1{Task version supported}
    V1 -->|no| FV[failed: task_version_unsupported]
    V1 -->|yes| L2[Layer 2: Domain gate]

    L2 --> DCHK1[Permission check]
    L2 --> DCHK2[Precondition check]
    L2 --> DCHK3[Conflict check]
    L2 --> DCHK4[Task-local preflight]

    DCHK1 --> L2A[Aggregate CheckResults]
    DCHK2 --> L2A
    DCHK3 --> L2A
    DCHK4 --> L2A

    L2A --> L2D{L2 decision}
    L2D -->|hard_block| F2[failed: domain hard block]
    L2D -->|soft_block| BC[blocked_confirmation]
    L2D -->|retry_hint| L3[Layer 3: Execution gate]
    L2D -->|pass| L3

    L3 --> G1{retry_count < max_retries}
    G1 -->|no and retry_hint| F3[failed: max_retries_exceeded]
    G1 -->|yes and retry_hint| RW[retry_waiting]
    G1 -->|pass| G2{autoconfirm mode}

    G2 -->|yes| R2[ready]
    G2 -->|no| BC

    RW --> BK[Persist backoff_ms and next_retry_at]
    BK --> PICKUP[Scheduler pickup after backoff]
    PICKUP --> P0

    BC --> TTL{TTL expired}
    TTL -->|yes| F4[failed: blocked_confirmation_timeout]
    TTL -->|no| U1[User confirm or clarification]
    U1 --> REPRE[Rebuild PreflightRequest]
    REPRE --> L1

    R1 --> S0{Scheduler lock}
    R2 --> S0
    S0 -->|slot free| X1[running]
    S0 -->|slot busy| WAIT[stay ready]
    WAIT --> S0

    X1 --> EX[Executor with prepared_input]
    EX --> ER{Execution result}
    ER -->|success| SUC[succeeded]
    ER -->|transient error| RW2[retry_waiting]
    ER -->|domain error recoverable| OBS[Observation builder]
    ER -->|terminal error| FAILX[failed]

    RW2 --> BK2[Persist execution backoff]
    BK2 --> S0

    SUC --> OBS
    FAILX --> OBS
    F1 --> OBS
    FV --> OBS
    F2 --> OBS
    F3 --> OBS
    F4 --> OBS

    OBS --> REP{Repair needed}
    REP -->|yes| NP[Planner append-only repair step]
    REP -->|no| GOAL{Goal reached}
    NP --> B
    GOAL -->|yes| END[Final synthesis]
    GOAL -->|no| NP

    AUD[(Immutable preflight audit log)]
    L1 -.-> AUD
    V1 -.-> AUD
    L2A -.-> AUD
    L3 -.-> AUD
    BC -.-> AUD
    RW -.-> AUD
    EX -.-> AUD
    OBS -.-> AUD

    style SUC fill:#2d6a4f,color:#fff
    style END fill:#1d3557,color:#fff
    style BC fill:#e9c46a,color:#000
    style RW fill:#f4a261,color:#000
    style RW2 fill:#f4a261,color:#000
    style F1 fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style FV fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style F2 fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style F3 fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style F4 fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style FAILX fill:#9b2226,color:#fff